<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yswʿ rby ạ̉ḥmd</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yasūʿa rabĩy ạảḥ̊madu
 walạis̊mihi ạủsabĩḥu
 nasẖīdī ladẖãẗuⁿ lahu
 wāảnā bihi ạảf̊raḥu

[V2]
 2- ạủgẖanĩy lahu kulã ḥīn̊
 mā dum̊tu ạảnā fī ạl̊wujūd̊
 ại̹nãhu sayĩdī ạlạảmīn̊
 wah̊wa ạl̊ḥabību wāl̊wadūd̊

[V3]
 3- fah̊wa fī sẖakẖ̊ṣihi ʿajīb̊
 kadẖā fī ḥubĩhi farīd̊
 ại̹dẖ̊ qad̊ fadānī biạlṣãlīb̊
 yā lahu min̊ ḥubiⁿ̃ sẖadīd̊

[V4]
 4- fakulã daẙnī qad̊ wafay̱
 wāl̊ʿad̊lu hakadẖā ạk̊tafay̱
 wafīhi lī kulũ ạk̊tifā
 fah̊wa naṣībī wakafay̱</lyrics>
</song>